I thought it was about the challenge?  Guess its about the loot huh?<br>
<br>
If CT is up on the day you have a raid schedule then he's yours.  SR/Watchers don't go charging into the plane 1 hour after servers come up like they do on other servers.  If your raid happens to fall on a day of a patch or CT's respawn etc then you get your shot.  Tuesday Puma's fear raid will have CT spawn during the night before their raid.  Puma has his chance at God items just like you would if you happened to have the plane reserved.  Go sign up for his raid and you have a chance too.  SR/Watchers isn't going to go in an hour before his raid and kill CT.  Unlike other servers they respect people. <br>
<br>
If Puma wishes to allow SR/Watchers to come into the plane on HIS day to take down CT/Draco thats PUMA'S choice.  Its his plane to do whatever he wants with.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uthoricthemad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Thoric the Mad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Brell's man of Nomex</span><br>  Posts: 223<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/27/01 12:46:19 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Re</span><hr size=1> Sheebla, you can do exactly what we do. Organize a raid crew, talk to the raid leader the night CT is up and ask them if they object to you taking a shot at it. NOBODY is stopping you but you. Is there really a problem here besides you being too lazy to do the footwork? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usindarreofbrell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sindarre of Brell</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 186<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/27/01 6:34:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Re</span><hr size=1> No you don't have to come with us Sheebla.<br>
<br>
Here is what you need to do:<br>
<br>
1) make friends of people around your level<br>
2) add your friends and your guildmembers together and hope for a number greater then or equal to 30.<br>
3) put them in groups of six.. try to have clerics to heal, shamans to buff, warriors to tank, and nukers to nuke.<br>
4) for cazic you don't even need to worry about resists even.<br>
5) make other friends or talk constructively with the people in fear.<br>
6) get buffed<br>
7) yell Charge!! this is when you and your friends run up and attempt to kill cazic<br>
<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  congradulate yourself on your victory.. distribute spoils.  OR<br>
9) discuss why you did not win.. and how you can better yourselves for the next attempt.<br>
<br>
Tell me what on that list you cannot accomplish.  Yes this post is sorta sarcastic but this is not brain surgery hun.  Tell me why you can't do this.. you keep telling us what a great raid crew you have and how you could kill klandicar and veeshans and cazic.  DO IT.  Quit posting, organize your groups and go kill Cazic.  Veeshan's has not been touched for about a month... just go.  Inny, Yelniak, Lord Tormax, Vindicator, Sontalak, POG, Veeshan's peak, Wuoshi, Gorenaire, Talendor.. all of them are probably up right now waiting for someone to try them.  And if one of them is not.. wait a few days and they will be.<br>
<br>
